org.openhab.binding.velux.internal.things

Class VeluxScene

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openhab.binding.velux.internal.things.VeluxScene

  • @NonNullByDefault
public class VeluxScene
extends java.lang.Object
    Velux scene representation.

    Combined set of information with references towards multiple Velux product states.

    Methods in handle this type of information:

    • VeluxScene(String, int, boolean, VeluxProductState[]) to create a new scene.
    • VeluxScene(VeluxScene) to duplicate a scene.
    • getName() to retrieve the name of this scene.
    • getBridgeSceneIndex() to retrieve the index of this scene.
    • toString() to retrieve a human-readable description of this scene.
    Author:
    Guenther Schreiner - initial contribution.
    See Also:
    VeluxProductState
